text:
Splash News

There's only one Jennifer Lopez--her talent, beauty and sensuality are truly irreplacable and inigualable. There's no denying that there will never be another one like the multi-talented superstar but there are women out there who share a striking resemblance to the Puerto Rican singer. It's crazy to see some of these doubles' pictures--sometimes you won't even know who you're actually looking at, if at the Bronx Diva or any of her twins! When scrolling through the gallery, you'll feel as if you're seeing double!

More from MamásLatinas: Jennifer Lopez's 35 best stage looks of all time

There have been many comparisons between the Shades of Blue actress and her look-alikes through the years, and there are definitely some that will make you do a double take. True, being in the public eye does make other women aspire to look and dress like you, as happens with Jennifer Lopez. However, some of these women go beyond mere imitation--there are celebs, fans and even one bodybuilder who can pass off as the singer's doppelgänger. It's uncanny!

Besides some women who naturally just look like Jennifer, some of these women have had surgical enhancements to look like the Latina superstar. But the fortunate ones are the ones who were just born with incredible look like Jennifer's. Click through to see photos of nine women that might easily be confused as Jenny from the Block.
title: 9 Jennifer Lopez look-alikes that have us seeing double
